parameters.message: Where is he?
I think I'm gonna look for him.
As I walk towards the bathroom, I find a track of vomit going to the exit door.
I follow it.
I'm outside, and I can see him, with a new shirt on, sitting on the curb.
"Hey Keisuke! What happened?"
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Hameru Tabe!!! I missed you. You are my friend, aren't you?"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Yes! I was waiting for you on the kitchen!" - I sit beside him.
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Oh... I forgot that..."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Usually I come outside... Because of the fresh air... And... And..."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: He rests his head on my shoulder. Hope he doesn't puke on me...
"And... well... that's about it..."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Yeah, that's a good thing to do when you are sick..."
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Noooo maaaan! You are siiiick! I'm a dork!"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "That's not the kind of sick I meant..."
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Dork. Dork. Dork is a weird word, right?"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Oh damn... here we go... Drunk-talk..."
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Yes! Drunk talk! Fuck it. Fuck this school, fuck the food, fuck everything... Oooh! Speaking of fucking the food...."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: WHAT? DOES HE KNOW WHAT I DID? IT WAS ONE TIME ONLY! SHIT! I'LL NEVER DO IT AGAIN!
"Did you know... that there's a food fucker on this school?"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: SHIT.
"Yeeeeees... I heard he attacked five times last month.."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "One time, I found the fucked food. It was a Taco. It was filled with cum. GUACUM MOLE. HAHAHAHAHA"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: Wait. I did not fuck a Taco. Is there another food fucker? Is that what I am now? A food fucker?
"haha... GUACUM MOLE... That was terrible, wasn't it?"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Is there really a food fucker?"
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Oh yes... sorry for the bad joke.. but I really found that Taco. I almost ate it. Gross. I get sick just remembering it..."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "... Blaaargh"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: He puked again. Glad he moved his head on the opposite side from where I'm sitting.
But hey... Maybe I'm not so weird... Maybe food fucking is a common practice between chefs worldwide.
"Hey man... I think I'm going to sleep now, okay?"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Let's go inside, I'll take you to your room... Oh wait... Where's your room?"
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Just beside yours..."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: That explains why he was trying to open my door...
I would try (and fail) to carry him, but he is managing to drag himself, I think I just need to steer him on the right directions.
That was tiring, but he is safe and sound inside his room. And I am on mine.
Time to sleep, finally. It's almost morning already...
